*在[[英聯邦|英聯邦]]國家的[[國殤紀念日|陣亡將士紀念日]]中，會經常出現該曲。<ref name="BBC News051114">{{en}}{{cite news |title=The sound of silence |publisher=BBC News |date=2005-11-14 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/magazine/4429278.stm |accessdate=2007-04-20 |archive-date=2008-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080115075512/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/magazine/4429278.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
